This project involves a traffic and pedestrian light system that includes a pedestrian button for crossing the road.

When the button is pressed, the pedestrian light switches to green as quickly as possible. The pedestrian signal 

remains red when the traffic light is green, and when the pedestrian signal turns green, the traffic light switches to red.


Link to the Wokwi project.

https://wokwi.com/projects/462223153324079105
